JOB DESCRIPTION
 Lead a team in managing new product development for precision metal engineering.
 Lead and prepare quotations for new projects.
 Work with sales team to bid and win new projects
 Manage the entire product development process in new projects
 Be the main liaison person in communicating and coordinating between customers and company in relation to new and existing projects.
 Review and interpret technical drawings in precision metal engineering.

REQUIREMENTS
 Diploma / Degree in Business, Mechanical Engineering or related discipline
 Min 5 years working experience in Project Management in manufacturing industry
 Experience in precision metal engineering preferred
 Strong technical skills and experience with reading technical drawings
 Excellent presentation, communication and interpersonal skills
 Ability to work on tight deadlines
 Meticulous and detailed oriented
 Good team player
 Experience in managing a team
 Proficiency in Microsoft Excel / Word / PowerPoint